            "title": "黑期重越二萬六 高水約180點 小米ADR昨晚則跌逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英偉達上季業績與本季指引均高於預期，帶動美股期指與亞洲外圍股市造好，為港股添加反彈動力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-ap_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時15分升197點或0.76%，報26011點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR指數報25741點，較香港上日現貨收市低89點或0.35%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣619.6元，較上日香港收市低2.88元或0.46%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣154.7元，較上日香港收市高0.1元或0.06%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合港幣97.4元，較上日香港收市低1.16元或1.18%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合港幣112.5元，較上日香港收市低1.85元或1.62%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合港幣38.6元，較上日香港收市低2.18元或5.34%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123043__source-web_01810-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123043__source-web_01810-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合港幣107.7元，較上日香港收市低0.09元或0.09%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合港幣78.2元，較上日香港收市低0.39元或0.49%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣415.5元，較上日香港收市低0.94元或0.22%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合港幣58元，較上日香港收市低0.25元或0.43%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣8.1元，較上日香港收市低0.01元或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25820點，跌2點，較上日恒指收市25830點，低水11點。科指期貨夜市收報5584點，較上日科指收市低水23點；國指期貨夜市收報9140點，較上日國指收市低水11點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15441033-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e5%85%ad-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%84180%e9%bb%9e-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3adr%e6%98%a8%e6%99%9a%e5%89%87%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-20 08:20:33",
