            "title": "A股午後弱  深股險守萬三關  成交縮減",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午波幅擴大，深股險守13000關，兩市合計成交17259.09億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日升6點或0.18%，報3946點，今早以3937點開市，跌1點或0.05%，午後波幅擴大，低見3930，跌9點或0.23%，為全日低位，後段見3960，升21點或0.53%，為全日高位，半日成交7209.09億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日跌0.4點，報13080，今天開市報13071點，亦跌8點或0.07%，最高報13164，升84點或0.64%，即急速向下，午後見13009，跌71點或0.54%，為全日低位，全日成交10050億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日報4588，升20點或0.44%，今早開跌不足1點或，開報4568點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報3076，升7點或0.25%，今早開市報3065點，跌4點或0.13%。</p>\n</div>",
